\par <h> <#/>PSYCHO-ACTIVE DRUGS </h>
\par <#/>Man has used and abused drugs since the beginning of civilization. <#/>During the last few decades of the twentieth century, there has been a marked increase in the use of psycho-active or mind-altering drugs.
