for purposes other than the one intended, it is known as drug misuse, for example using piriton tablets in higher dosage to induce sleep. <#/>When one uses drugs for non medical purposes persistently and for his own intended reasons, it is known as drug a
buse. <#/>When this occurs beyond the will and control of the individual and is used persistently and excessively for non-medial purposes, then this condition is known as drug addiction or drug dependence.}{\v\f0\fs24\lang2057 
