}{\f0\fs24\lang2057 and }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 L.tropica. L. donovani }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 also causes post kala-azar dermal leishmaniasis. <#/>}{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 Leishmania major }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 has been isolated only from rodents}{
\v\f0\fs24\lang2057  (Chance et al., 1978; Githure et al., 1984; Mutinga and Ngoka, 1983).}{\f0\fs24\lang2057 
