area adjacent to Nairobi District. <#/>It was important to carry out a survey of existing phlebotomine sandflies in Nairobi and to determine their vector potential. <#/>Two genera of sandflies namely, }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 Phlebotomus }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 
and }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 Sergentomyia }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 were recorded during this study. <#/>Vector studies in Kenyan foci have shown that termited-welling sandfly species of the genus }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 Phlebotomus, }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 
