\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 martini, }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 are vectors of visceral leishmaniasis and which are cave dwellers, }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 P. Iongipes, P. pedifer,P. elgonensis }{\f0\fs24\lang2057 and }{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 P}{\f0\fs24\lang2057 . }{
